com.ebay.lightning.core.manager

Class TaskExecutionManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ebay.lightning.core.manager.TaskExecutionManager

  • @Component
public class TaskExecutionManager
extends Object
    The TaskExecutionManager provides the actual implementation of request processing, reporting and storage. The requests are queued up and gets processed in FIFO order. THe class delegates report storage to ExecutionDataStore
    Author:
    shashukla
